Package com.teamone.unitask.timeslots

Class TimeSlotController

java.lang.Object
com.teamone.unitask.timeslots.TimeSlotController
@CrossOrigin(origins="http://localhost:3000", maxAge=3600L, allowCredentials="true") @RestController @RequestMapping("/api/test") public class TimeSlotController extends Object
Rest Controller for managing time slots associated with projects. This controller handles operations such as retrieving, creating, deleting, and finding common time slots for a given project.
